      "updated": 1782884779444,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Lambda Auto-Scaling: \nNumber of active message groups  →  AWS auto-scales Lambda",
      "fontSize": 12.577745225694427,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Lambda Auto-Scaling: \nNumber of active message groups  →  AWS auto-scales Lambda",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 268,
      "versionNonce": 687159685,
      "index": "af",
      "seed": 1,
      "frameId": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "scale-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 357.6673583984375,
      "y": 827,
      "width": 695.865234375,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782884431035,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": ": up to +60 new instances/minute, max 1,000 concurrent (account limit)\nWith SQS FIFO: at most 1 Lambda instance per active MessageGroup  →  same order is always sequential regardless of fleet size\nDifferent MessageGroupIds (different OrderIds)  →  fully parallel  →  throughput scales linearly with number of distinct active orders\nTo cap scale-out for this queue: set  ScalingConfig.MaximumConcurrency  on the SQS event source mapping",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": ": up to +60 new instances/minute, max 1,000 concurrent (account limit)\nWith SQS FIFO: at most 1 Lambda instance per active MessageGroup  →  same order is always sequential regardless of fleet size\nDifferent MessageGroupIds (different OrderIds)  →  fully parallel  →  throughput scales linearly with number of distinct active orders\nTo cap scale-out for this queue: set  ScalingConfig.MaximumConcurrency  on the SQS event source mapping",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "version": 46,
      "versionNonce": 1811902091,
      "index": "ag",
      "seed": 1,
      "frameId": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
